oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Burn. Newell Sanders telegram.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Newell Sanders, Chattanooga, Tenn., handwritten telegram to Harry Burn, Niota, Tenn. "So glad to hear that you have been re-elected. Congratulations. Newell Sanders."
